ings":["Some characteristic forenames:  German Ernst, Hans, Juergen, Jutta, Volker.","German:","topographic name from Middle High German <i>wēc</i> ‘path, street’, or a habitational name from any of various places called with this word."]},{"name":"Wedeking","meanings":["Some characteristic forenames:  German Kurt, Erwin, Horst.","German (Westphalia): patronymic from   Wedekind  ."]},{"name":"Wettig","meanings":["German: derivative of <b>Wetting</b>, a patronymic (ending in <i>-ing</i>) from personal names formed with <i>wid(u)</i> ‘wood, forest’ as the first element, for instance   Wedekind  ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Wedekind von Stumpenhausen was born in 1140, in Wildeshausen, Oldenburg, Lower Saxony, Germany as the son of Gero von Versfleth. He had at least 1 son with Christine von Oldenburg. He died in 1180, in Hannover, Lower Saxony, Germany, at the age of 40."},"et":{"1140–1180":"1140–1180","1144–1234":"1144–1234","1162–Male":"1162–Surnud","1070–1165":"1070–1165","AFT 1165":"pärast 1165","1234":"1234","1144":"1144","1165":"1165","1140":"1140","1162":"1162","1180":"1180","1070":"1070","Hoya, Hannover, Niedersachsen, Germany":"Hannover, Niedersachsen, Saksamaa","Wildeshausen, Oldenburg, Niedersachsen, Germany":"Wildeshausen, Landkreis Oldenburg, Niedersachsen, Saksamaa","Stumpenhausen, Deutschland":"Saksamaa"},"fi":{"1140–1180":"1140–1180","1144–1234":"1144–1234","1162–Male":"1162–Kuollut","1070–1165":"1070–1165","AFT 1165":"1165 jälkeen","1234":"1234","1144":"1144","1165":"1165","1140":"1140","1162":"1162","1180":"1180","1070":"1070","Hoya, Hannover, Niedersachsen, Germany":"Hannover, Niedersachsen, Saksa","Wildeshausen, Oldenburg, Niedersachsen, Germany":"Wildeshausen, Landkreis Oldenburg, Niedersachsen, Saksa","Stumpenhausen, Deutschland":"Saksa"},"fr":{"1140–1180":"1140–1180","1144–1234":"1144–1234","1162–Male":"1162–Décédé","1070–1165":"1070–1165","AFT 1165":"après 1165","1234":"1234","1144":"1144","1165":"1165","1140":"1140","1162":"1162","1180":"1180","1070"